     1	//! Generate an HTML visualization for a rhei plan (or workspace of plans).
     2	//!
     3	//! Dogfoods the `rhei viz` command specified in
     4	//! [`docs/specs/rhei-viz.spec.md`](../../../docs/specs/rhei-viz.spec.md)
